csExportItem zDocsExportTopicButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"singlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportSubtopicsButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"pdfWithChildren\" role=\"button\">Save selected topic and subtopics</a><a class=\"zDocsExportItem zDocsExportBundleButton\" href=\"#\" id=\"wholeBundlePdf\" role=\"button\">Save entire publication</a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicShare zDocsShareButton\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-expanded=\"false\" aria-label=\"Share\" class=\"d-none d-lg-flex zDocsShareDialogButton\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" data-tooltip-content=\"Share\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none zDocsShareDialogButton\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-share\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-share\"></use></svg>Share</span><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu\"><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareEmail\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Email Link</span></a><a class=\"dropdown-item zDocsShareButton zDocsShareLink\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\"><span>Copy Link</span></a></div></div><div class=\"zDocsFeedback zDocsFeedback zDocsTopicFeedback\" role=\"listitem\"><span aria-label=\"Feedback\" class=\"zDocsFeedbackButton d-none d-lg-flex\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2529012\" data-toggle=\"modal\" data-tooltip-content=\"Feedback\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsTopicActionsTooltip\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg></span><span class=\"d-lg-none d-flex zDocsFeedbackButton\" data-backdrop=\"static\" data-return-focus=\"#zDocsTopicActionsMobile\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_main_2529012\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Juli 11, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104jrg1665702752411.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jrg1665702752411.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/jrg1665702752411.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"jrg1665702752411\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      $page\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body conbody\" id=\"jrg1665702752411___page_279617\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Return the current page number in a Report or Form while printing.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"jrg1665702752411__topic_d87392e1_d87393e1_d87394e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jrg1665702752411__p_d87395e1_d87396e1_d87397e1\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$page</span>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"jrg1665702752411__section_w445ab1b7b5_w446ab1b7_w447ab1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jrg1665702752411__p_d87398e1_d87399e1_d87400e1\">Example: <code class=\"ph codeph\">if ($page != 1)</code> ...</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jrg1665702752411__topic_d58212e1_d58213e1_d58214e1_d58215e1_d58216e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d715613e75\">\n                       \n Return Values\n </h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"jrg1665702752411__table_d9338e1_d9339e1_d9340e1\"><caption><span class=\"table--title-label\">Table 1. </span><span class=\"title\">Values returned in $page</span></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jrg1665702752411__table_d9338e1_d9339e1_d9340e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"jrg1665702752411__table_d9338e1_d9339e1_d9340e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Meaning</p>\n</th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jrg1665702752411__table_d9338e1_d9339e1_d9340e1__entry__1\">\n 0\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jrg1665702752411__table_d9338e1_d9339e1_d9340e1__entry__2\">Uniface is not printing (that is,\n                           <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$printing</span> is 0). </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jrg1665702752411__table_d9338e1_d9339e1_d9340e1__entry__1\">\n &gt;0\n </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"jrg1665702752411__table_d9338e1_d9339e1_d9340e1__entry__2\">\n Number of the page currently being printed.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jrg1665702752411__topic_d58217e1_d58218e1_d58219e1_d58220e1_d58221e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d715613e133\">Use</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jrg1665702752411__d6494e20\">Use in Form and Report components.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jrg1665702752411__topic_d58222e1_d58223e1_d58224e1_d58225e1_d58226e1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d715613e143\">\n                       \n Description\n </h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jrg1665702752411__p_d87413e1_d87414e1_d87415e1\">You can use <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$page</span> to assign the page number to fields in header or footer frames.</p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"jrg1665702752411__p_d87416e1_d87417e1_d87418e1\">If you are not printing, it returns zero when used in the getFocus trigger of a header or footer frame.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"jrg1665702752411__section_xmb_ryf_1cc\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d715613e158\">Example: Using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$page</span></h2>\n<div class=\"div\">\n<p class=\"p\">The ProcScript in the following example assigns the page number to the\n               dummy field REPORTPAGE in the footer frame. The footer frame has the\n                  <span class=\"ph uicontrol\">Suppress Print if Empty</span> property selected, which means that\n               it does not appear if REPORTPAGE has no value.</p>\n<p class=\"p\">The first page of the report is a cover sheet that is not numbered;\n               subsequent pages are numbered starting at 1. Because of the unnumbered page, the\n               value of REPORTPAGE is one less than the value supplied by\n               <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">$page</span>.</p>\n<div class=\"code-toolbar\"><pre class=\"pre language-plaintext\" id=\"jrg1665702752411__pre_a1l_ryf_1cc\" tabindex=\"0\"><code class=\"language-plaintext\">trigger getFocus ; of footer frame\n if ($page = 1) ;if on first page done ;take no action\n done\n else\n REPORTPAGE = $page - 1\n endif\nend</code></pre><div class=\"toolbar\"><div class=\"toolbar-item\"><button class=\"copy-to-clipboard-button\" data-copy-state=\"copy\" type=\"button\"><span>Copy</span></button></div></div></div>\n</div>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hxj1665702751771.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$lines</a><p>Return the number of lines remaining on the current page.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/biv1665702630863.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>trigger getFocus (Frame)</a><p>Trigger that responds to the frame getting focus (usually when the frame is about to be printed).</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529012\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_2529012\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "$page Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Juli 11, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 $page Return the current page number in a Report or Form while printing. $page Example: if ($page != 1) ... Return Values Table 1. Values returned in $page Value Meaning 0 Uniface is not printing (that is, $printing is 0). >0 Number of the page currently being printed. Use Use in Form and Report components. Description You can use $page to assign the page number to fields in header or footer frames. If you are not printing, it returns zero when used in the getFocus trigger of a header or footer frame. Example: Using $page The ProcScript in the following example assigns the page number to the dummy field REPORTPAGE in the footer frame. The footer frame has the Suppress Print if Empty property selected, which means that it does not appear if REPORTPAGE has no value. The first page of the report is a cover sheet that is not numbered; subsequent pages are numbered starting at 1. Because of the unnumbered page, the value of REPORTPAGE is one less than the value supplied by $page . trigger getFocus ; of footer frame if ($page = 1) ;if on first page done ;take no action done else REPORTPAGE = $page - 1 endif end Copy Related Links $lines Return the number of lines remaining on the current page. trigger getFocus (Frame) Trigger that responds to the frame getting focus (usually when the frame is about to be printed). Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}